StepA-1.Text:
We all have things we struggle with, studies show that going to detox is the number 1 way to get off drugs and or alcohol and to begin your path to recovery.  We have located detoxes in your area to consider with your peer mentor: 
{SearchForDetoxResults}

our peer mentor will help get you a spot and take you to the detox.  They will also make sure you have everything you need when you check in. The detox location will work with you to find a longer term rehab once you have completed detox but your peer mentor will be checking in with you regularly so just remember – YOU GOT THIS!
